name: Brocode
tagline: A Bro doesn't allow another Bro to struggle with web packaging tools.
body:
# brocode

A Bro doesn't allow another Bro to struggle with web packaging tools.

So here goes a browserify setup with multiple entry point.

## install

npm i -g brocode

## usage

brocode server

brocode build
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
